                <note rend="inline" type="source">651.116 Nitrate/75: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Straus</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-11-24T15:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 24, 1934—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>473. Your 869, November 23. So far as we can determine American nitrate interests
                    are not parties to the nitrate cartel, although there are indications that they
                    are on friendly terms with cartel members.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
